control over the restive territory with an army,

00:02:40.540 --> 00:02:44.440
turning the elite’s demands for autonomy
into a full-scale revolt for independence.

00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:53.800
On March 13, 1836, Santa Ana defeated the American
defenders of the Alamo, killing 187 (or 188, sources
